Maintainer: Fabrice Durand <fdurand@inverse.ca>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10), golang-go (>= 1.16), dh-systemd
Standards-Version: 4.1.3
Homepage: https://github.com/fdurand/standalone_dhcp

Package: godhcp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: High-performance standalone DHCP server
 A high-performance, multi-interface DHCP server written in Go.
 .
 Features:
  - Multiple network interface support
  - DHCP relay functionality
  - Static IP assignments
  - IP pool management with multiple algorithms
  - REST API for monitoring and management
  - Web-based configuration interface
  - Systemd integration
  - Real-time statistics and debugging
